    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Agricultural buildings designed to reduce labor, automate, and improve efficiency in milking cows. Several different designs are in use, but all parlors follow key components of milking procedures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
